Title: A-Gas Solstice N40 Oxygen Free Nitrogen Rental Cylinder 40ltr
Description: This A-Gas R448A Solstice N40 oxygen-free nitrogen rental cylinder contains a non-flammable HFO blend, an ideal replacement for R404A and R22 in low and medium temperature refrigeration applications. This zeotropic blend provides a low global warming potential (GWP) and high energy efficiency and offers a lower compressor discharge temperature in medium and low temperature conditions.
